# Input

```vue
<div v-for="  item     in    items  ">{{ item }}</div>
<div v-for="n   in      10">{{ n }}</div>
<div v-for="value     of     values">{{ value }}</div>

```


# Formatted

```vue
<div v-for="item in items">{{ item }}</div>
<div v-for="n in 10">{{ n }}</div>
<div v-for="value of values">{{ value }}</div>

```
